	   <tr><td colspan=2>I found out real quick that a wizard needs something better than the dagger he/she starts with.&nbsp;&nbsp;I suggest that once you get about level 5, go to Blackburrow with a group, and kill scrawny gnolls.  One of them drops a cracked staff, which hits for 5 damage.<br><br>When you can afford it, though, sell it and buy a better one, either a Great Staff (damage 7), or a Velium Great Staff (damage 36).  A warning, both of these are two handed, and you will need to take whatever light source you have out of your hand to equip the staff.<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
