	   <tr><td colspan=2>Paduval Caverns is the way to go. Zone in thru Shadeweaver thicket and start with the shrooms and little brown beatles. Then as they start getting easy move on up towards the water. Solo at first but once you hit the 20s you should group up at the bandit camps. At 24 or 25 get out and solo in OT or head over to SK solo there or head into Splitpaw and group. Oh yeah you can probably goto Neth Lair till 30 or so. You can move to DSP. Once you hit mid 30s try RM for cash and XP(this will be slow but you will have tons of money). 39 play with the big boys in DL or quad. Me i single pulled mobs root/nuked in DL till 50 I think. After that its KC if goodie race or ruin faction in OT and 1 neriak guard like me. Thats all i have for now.<br><br>Smackin Mobsaround<br>&lt;Merciless Elites&gt;<br>52nd season<br><br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
